Author:
Pengcheng Wan HashMap dependency hold all the dependent information: jobstatus and trigger For example, for JobD it has these information { {JobB, Success:Norun}} {JobC, Success:Norun} {schedule, daily} } HashMap matchMap hold all the above the condition satisfied alternatives. For example, for JobD it has these information { {JobB, false}} {JobC, false} {schedule, false} }
